{"tid":2310481,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"紅磡疑有人爬後巷水渠 (09:19)","createTime":"2020-12-03T09:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T13:33:55.000Z","uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b98cbe85a3278642fe914f5ab1c0ce0a61f77f","tid":2310481,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20201203/s00001/7ddc17d7c50ef45ceaf8e66fa04d9d4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20201203%2Fs00001%2F7ddc17d7c50ef45ceaf8e66fa04d9d4d.jpg&h=477f84b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201203/s00001/1606958534412/%e7%b4%85%e7%a3%a1%e7%96%91%e6%9c%89%e4%ba%ba%e7%88%ac%e5%be%8c%e5%b7%b7%e6%b0%b4%e6%b8%a0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201203%2Fs00001%2F1606958534412%2F%25e7%25b4%2585%25e7%25a3%25a1%25e7%2596%2591%25e6%259c%2589%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%2588%25ac%25e5%25be%258c%25e5%25b7%25b7%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e6%25b8%25a0&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPf3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=7309ba82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201203%2Fs00001%2F1606958534412%2F%25e7%25b4%2585%25e7%25a3%25a1%25e7%2596%2591%25e6%259c%2589%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%2588%25ac%25e5%25be%258c%25e5%25b7%25b7%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e6%25b8%25a0&h=4aee372c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201203/s00001/1606958534412/%e7%b4%85%e7%a3%a1%e7%96%91%e6%9c%89%e4%ba%ba%e7%88%ac%e5%be%8c%e5%b7%b7%e6%b0%b4%e6%b8%a0</a><br />\n早上7時許，警方接獲報案，稱有人在紅磡長寧街5號後巷爬水渠，警方到場後未有發現，案件列可疑人發現。"},{"pid":"59d42e889fc033c0ba43045dcf7303bab0f2953f","tid":2310481,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:47:28.000Z","msg":"房屋署拎廁所門比熱狗辦事處用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2276892\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2276892</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b0e66aca3457653385569ffd620b47b0fa2f5d45","tid":2310481,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:48:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sd75tXk0sFY?t=321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fsd75tXk0sFY%3Ft%3D321&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPf3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=c6602db2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sd75tXk0sFY?t=321</a><br />\n<em>鄭松泰議員：在香港理工大學被圍困的孩子他們其實很多也不是孩子，所以我不會濫用年青人這說法，無需每次都說是為了年青人或學生被圍困於香港理工大學的人，<span class=\"gold\">有報道指他們經水渠或游繩等方法想離開，我不知道有多少人，他們對這個政府的仇恨，你們等着瞧吧！<br />\n驕生慣養的香港人要竄入布滿曱甴、老鼠的地下水渠，爬行 1 小時逃走，為的是躲避警察的毆打，大家想想這仇恨是多麼的恐怖。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />這是林鄭月娥一手造成的，所以她的違法行為，簡單來說，她就是&quot;香港屠夫&quot;，在歷史上要留名，會被釘在十字架上。</em><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965a822ca8c84d65e9756bcb00bc8e8ebc37cc6c","tid":2310481,"uid":275498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:48:55.000Z","msg":"紅磡啲舊樓成日有人爬上去爆入屋偷野"},{"pid":"291a7e5be2e02a938d1af17f76e6b9176ab77a15","tid":2310481,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"港島人走到去紅磡爬渠？"},{"pid":"17acc718ab5d0a81976909dac8bb422c234b6ba7","tid":2310481,"uid":261505,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:30:34.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d574e1e57b8c73bf79e03fc34b7fd8e0d78f27c5","tid":2310481,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:36:02.000Z","msg":"四眼禮志爬上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8219bf82ef09c79988e0b9bb